Page_0: "Hammerite Compendium of Precepts, Regimens and Rules of Conduct, Vol. 97

Thou hast no eyes other than the Builder gave unto thee to see,
Thou hast no ears other than the Builder gave unto thee to hear,
Thou hast no flesh other than the Builder gave unto thee to wear"

Page_1: "Pledgest thou not to the unrighteous and demonesque that which thou dost not own and that which thou hast not created for thyself,
Failing worship of the of the true and one Builder, t'wil He reclaim that which He hath given unto thee"